title: Links
personal-links-text: Personal links give you the opportunity to invite partners to your team and increase the number of your followers. In this way you increase your profit and passive income.
links-clicked-tooltip: Number of clicks on your referral link
partners-tooltip: The number of users registered through your referral link
team-tooltip: The number of users registered through a referral link of one of your partners
personal-link-tooltip: Your referral link for inviting new partners.
personal-link-tooltip-2: Your link will become available after the purchase of the first level.
